# Aipify Master Structure Blueprint (Phase 500)

See [AIPIFY_MASTER_STRUCTURE_BLUEPRINT.md](../../AIPIFY_MASTER_STRUCTURE_BLUEPRINT.md) · [AIPIFY_PHASE500_MASTER_STRUCTURE_BLUEPRINT.md](../../AIPIFY_PHASE500_MASTER_STRUCTURE_BLUEPRINT.md).

**This blueprint supersedes ambiguous layer placement.** When older docs conflict, Phase 500 wins.

## Core hierarchy

```
SUPER ADMIN → PLATFORM → APP / PARTNERS → EMPLOYEES
```

**Principle:** PLATFORM sells · APP operates · EMPLOYEES use · PARTNERS sell.

**Customer ownership:** Customers belong to **Platform**. Partners receive attribution only.

## Five layers

| Layer | Route | Code | Who |
|-------|-------|------|-----|
| **SUPER ADMIN** | `/super/*` | `app/super/`, `lib/super-admin/` | Aipify Group AS only |
| **PLATFORM** | `/platform/*` | `app/platform/`, `lib/platform/` | Platform operators |
| **APP** | `/app/*` | `app/app/`, `lib/app/` | Customer organizations |
| **EMPLOYEES** | `/app/*` (role-scoped) | Same as APP | Users inside APP |
| **PARTNERS** | `/partners/*` | `app/partners/`, `lib/partners-portal/` | Growth Partners |

**Install Engine:** `/api/install/*`, `/api/embed/*` — APP-owned embedded layer (`lib/install/`, `lib/embed/`).

## Before every feature

1. Declare layer: SUPER ADMIN · PLATFORM · APP · EMPLOYEES · PARTNERS
2. Run placement check: `validateFeaturePlacement()` from `lib/core/master-structure/`
3. If unclear → **stop** — architecture review required

## Business Pack model

PLATFORM sells → APP purchases → APP activates → APP grants → EMPLOYEES use.

Pack UI owner: **APP**. Global pack governance: **PLATFORM**.

## License hierarchy

| APP status | Employee access |
|------------|-----------------|
| Active / Trial | Active |
| Suspended | Suspended |
| Cancelled | Disabled |

Employees **never** own licenses. APP is always the customer.

## Must never

- Customers or Partners access Super Admin
- Partners own customers (attribution only)
- Employees purchase packs or manage subscriptions
- Features without clear layer ownership ship without review

## Code

`lib/core/master-structure/` — `layers.ts`, `license-hierarchy.ts`, `business-pack-model.ts`, `validate-placement.ts`
